{"id": 1630, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些东西说是要帮你“把生活变简单”，结果却搞得更复杂？", "description": "能把简单的东西搞复杂，复杂的东西搞更复杂，你们可真是不简单！", "record_count": 5278, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170416013714aWRTnEy21DvqclFh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-19T03:00:23Z", "options": [{"id": 194304, "content": "难道不是手机吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 794033}, {"id": 194305, "content": "淘宝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991713}, {"id": 194306, "content": "互联网", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009176}, {"id": 194818, "content": "介入，就是混乱的根源。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 872003}, {"id": 194563, "content": "很多东西，就比如说普通的洗衣机等家用电器，本来说是解放双手，现在却使原先的一周洗一到两次变为每天，反而增加了更多的劳动量。\n再比如说手机，现在手机使联系变得更为便利，却使感情变得淡了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977162}, {"id": 195075, "content": "谈恋爱......我没谈过是不是不能说话?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011018}, {"id": 194309, "content": "说工具广告的，做工具的人喝西北风就饱了？你充过会员，买过软件么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443697}, {"id": 204296, "content": "腾讯游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1031657}, {"id": 194313, "content": "今天说好倒垃圾，结果我一回来垃圾没倒，反而外卖就多了几十个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986031}, {"id": 194315, "content": "嗯嗯嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713118}, {"id": 195083, "content": "谈恋爱\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981499}, {"id": 194316, "content": "嗯嗯嗯", "image": "img/option/option/20170419175851AkeQZ02UXI4itEYp", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713118}, {"id": 194572, "content": "手机剥奇了人与人面对面的交流！也剥夺了简单的生活！", "image": nu